summary: An ordinance providing for the payment of the cost and expense of the laying off, altering and establishing of Sycamore Avenue and 2nd Avenue Northwest, each from the north line of Electric Motor Line Addition to North 73rd Street, of 3rd Avenue Northwest, from the north line of Electric Motor Line Addition, to North 74th Street; of 1st Avenue Northwest, from North 73rd Street to North 74th Street, all in the City of Seattle.
